The new methods are:

``` c++
ui::ScrollView::stopAutoScroll();
extension::ScrollView::stopAnimatedContentOffset();
```

These methods effectively do the same thing, but are named in correlation to the methods that initiated the auto scroll.

Also made all the `ui::ScrollView::scrollTo*` methods `virtual`, which mirrors the functionality already present in the `jumpTo*` methods.

